      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 3915: Running a full reachable-history/blob validation during every conversation load can become expensive for large conversations and many accounts, because it walks every commit/tree/blob reachable from HEAD before startup can publish the conversation. Consider using libgit2\u0027s object database/graph validation primitives if available, limiting this deep validation to suspected repositories, or persisting a successful validation marker keyed by HEAD/pack state so unchanged repositories do not pay the full cost every startup.",
